column3: I'm Infyil. You're new, aren't you?
Kinda. But I wouldn't fret over it. You'll fit in in no time.
Do you know the others around here?
Know them? I practically am them. I know everybody who's anybody here and everywhere.
column7: ((RequirementType=None,RequirementValue=0.000000,Text="Then do you know Angel?",JumpTo="info_angel",EventName="""")),(RequirementType=None,RequirementValue=0.000000,Text="Do you know Dreamer?",JumpTo="info_dreamer",EventName=""""),(RequirementType=None,RequirementValue=0.000000,Text="Are you familiar with Mezco?",JumpTo="info_mezcos",EventName=""""),(RequirementType=None,RequirementValue=0.000000,Text="Have you met the maintenance worker?",JumpTo="info_worker",EventName="""")

column3: She's my granddaughter. Of course I know her.
She was saying something weird about waking up. Does that mean anything to you?
No, but then again, she's always saying the strangest things. I wouldn't take it too seriously if I were you.
Do I look like I wander maintenance halls in my free time?
Has he ever thought about leaving?
Leaving? Have you been talking to him about that? That fool's got enough of that from his sister. You stay outta that. You don't even know him.
Mezco? I think I've talked to him a few times.
